== News and Chronology ==

 * 2005-06-21 EU [http://www.ueapme.org/docs/press_releases/pr_2005/050621_Computer_Patent.pdf UEAPME: Parliament proposal on software patents would hit small firms]
 * 2005-04-27 EU [:Ueapme050427En: UEAPME (represents 11 million European SMEs) supports Mr. Rocard's preliminary report]
 * 2005-04-13 EU [http://www.beuc.org/Content/Default.asp?PageID=103 BEUC (European-wide consumer organisation) asks EP to restore first reading results, safeguard interoperability]
 * 2005-04-07 phm proposes [:MepsQuest05En: 5-step Questionnaire/Checklist for Software Patent Legislators]
 * 2005-03-28 [:LtrFfiiMeps050329En: FFII distributes a letter with appendices on paper to all MEPs]

